last_episode_to_air.name: Joy, Joy, Joy, Joy
last_episode_to_air.overview: Camille brings her vision to life, Tye finds love in an unexpected place, Quinn and Angie make amends, and the ladies get a surprise.

name: Harlem
overview: Four stylish and ambitious best girlfriends in Harlem, New York City: a rising star professor struggling to make space for her love life; a savvy tech entrepreneur always dating someone new; a no-filter singer; and a hopeless romantic fashion designer. Together, they level up into the next phase of their careers, relationships, and big city dreams.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: In season two, after blowing up her career and disrupting her love life, Camille has to figure out how to put the pieces back together; Tye considers her future; Quinn goes on a journey of self-discovery; and Angie’s career takes a promising turn.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: Just as Camille thinks she's in total control of her life, her ex shows up on her block making her question her choices. Tye receives an acquisition offer on her app. Angie questions what her next career step will be. Quinn has a rough night on Long Island.

episodes.name: Saturn Returns
episodes.overview: Tye is invited to do a Forbes interview, and decides to end things with Shayla. Angie is offered a role in a musical. Quinn struggles to make ends meet as the rent increases for her store. Camille’s boss tells her some bad news and she crosses paths with Ian at a friend’s engagement party.

episodes.name: Rainbow Sprinkles
episodes.overview: The girls try to cheer up Camille after the news of Ian's engagement. Tye has an awkward connection to her Forbes interviewer. Angie hits it off with her Uber driver. Quinn meets a new prospect on a dating app.

episodes.name: Winter Solstice
episodes.overview: Dr. Pruitt invites Camille to speak on a panel. A male stripper catches Quinn's eye. Tye struggles with a hair crisis. And Angie tells a lie to get a nanny job.

episodes.name: Boundaries
episodes.overview: Camille goes to Ian’s parents' going away party. Tye and Anna give things a try. Quinn attempts to keep things casual with Sean.

episodes.name: Cuffing Season
episodes.overview: Angie tries to track down a man to keep her warm for the winter. Jameson and Camille talk about what's next for them before a text sends her spiraling. Quinn takes Sean as her date to an event for Isabelle. Tye faces a health scare.

episodes.name: The Strong Black Woman
episodes.overview: Tye tries to get her health in order before an important conference. Camille questions how to respond to a strange text from Ian. Angie struggles with an ignorant cast member. Quinn navigates her mother's expectations.

episodes.name: Five Years Ago
episodes.overview: In this flashback episode, we see where our band of women were five years ago, when Ian left New York without Camille.

episodes.name: Secrets
episodes.overview: Camille secretly helps Ian out with a project. The women go to see Angie in the dress rehearsal of Get Out: The Musical. Quinn tries to win over Sean’s son.

episodes.name: Once Upon a Time in Harlem
episodes.overview: Dr. Pruitt's choice for Camille's dream job causes Camille to question her life choices. Tye fights to finalize her divorce. Angie gets offered a bigger role in the musical. Quinn confronts her feelings for Isabella.

episodes.name: Takesie Backsies
episodes.overview: Picking up where season one left off, Camille and Ian find themselves at a Crossroads, Quinn prepares for her first same-sex date, Angie tries to end her bad luck streak, and Tye tries to make a real connection.

episodes.name: If You Can't Say Anything Nice...
episodes.overview: Camille faces Jameson, Tye finds out she’s on a cautionary dating website, Angie finds luck in real estate, and Quinn explores her relationship with Isabela.

episodes.name: As Assist from the Sidelines
episodes.overview: Camille and Ian spend the day getting out of their heads with the help of too many edibles, Angie finds comfort with her extended family at home, Quinn drops big news at the golf course with her parents, and Tye studies the ideal relationship.

episodes.name: Baby and the Bath Water
episodes.overview: Camille and Ian have a scare, Tye is forced to start making decisions regarding her health, Quinn prepares for the biggest interview of her career, and Angie meets a new guy.

episodes.name: Pride
episodes.overview: Camille is summoned by Dr. Pruitt, Tye is Quinn’s reluctant tour guide for her first PRIDE as a member of the community, and Angie waits for an important call.

episodes.name: Out of the Deadpan and into the Fire
episodes.overview: Camille finds herself caught between Ian and Jameson yet again, Tye faces the reality of a big life decision, Quinn struggles with her recent losses, and Angie gets another big break.

episodes.name: Fall Back to Rumspringa Forward
episodes.overview: Camille, Quinn, Tye and Angie embark on a much-needed Girls Trip.

episodes.name: Joy, Joy, Joy, Joy
episodes.overview: Camille brings her vision to life, Tye finds love in an unexpected place, Quinn and Angie make amends, and the ladies get a surprise.
